       &mt LGUI C  &mt LALT R  &mt LSHIFT I  &mt LCTRL E  &kp O        &kp M      &mt LCTRL N  &mt LSHIFT T  &mt LEFT_ALT S  &mt LEFT_GUI H
&none  &kp V       &kp X       &kp J         &kp SQT      &kp GRAVE    &kp P      &kp F        &kp COMMA     &lt 5 DOT       &kp K           &lt 7 RIGHT_SHIFT
